# Laravel Auto CRUD - Coding Rules for Cursor AI

This file contains coding rules and guidelines for the Laravel Auto CRUD package. Follow these patterns when generating or modifying code in this package.

## Package Overview

Laravel Auto CRUD is a package that automatically generates complete CRUD scaffolding including controllers, requests, resources, services, policies, factories, routes, views, and Pest tests for Eloquent models.

